data.description: One of a Kind Home in Travilla Ventana Ranch. One Owner 4 Bedroom, Open Floor Plan, Raylee Home, 2+Living Areas, Dining Room, BreakFast Nook, Large Loft, Built-In Central Vacuum System, Refrigerated AC, Heated Underground Pool w' Cover.  Master Bedroom Retreat: Walk In Closet, Double Sided Fireplace, Shower, Tub and Exterior Balcony. 3 Car Garage. Extended Driveway. Back Yard Double Gate. Large Shed. Over Quarter Acre 3 lots in 1 =0.28 Acre at end of Culdesac. Newly: Synthetic Re-Stucco, Wood Re-Stain. Interior: New White Dove Painted Walls, Laminate Flooring/Tile. Ventana Ranch Amenities: Community Center, Pool, Tennis Court, Volleyball Court and Walking Trails throughout. Same Day Showings
